OL,3,CLamine Yamal could be investigated for
OL,4,Creportedly hiring people with dwarfism
OL,6,FSpain's Prosecutor's Office has been
OL,7,Fasked by the Ministry of Social Rights
OL,8,Fto investigate footballer Lamine
OL,9,FYamal, after he allegedly hired people
OL,10,Fwith dwarfism "solely for
OL,11,Fentertainment" at his 18th birthday
OL,12,Fparty.
OL,14,FThe Barcelona winger celebrated his
OL,15,Fbirthday on Sunday, but the
OL,16,Ffestivities have since been
OL,17,Fovershadowed in controversy.
