OL,3,CLamine Yamal could be investigated for
OL,4,Creportedly hiring people with dwarfism
OL,6,FThe Association of People with
OL,7,FAchondroplasia and other Skeletal
OL,8,FDysplasias with Dwarfism (ADEE) has
OL,9,F"publicly denounced" the hiring of
OL,10,Fpeople with dwarfism "as part of the
OL,11,Fentertainment".
OL,13,FThey announced they would launch legal
OL,14,Faction, saying Yamal's alleged actions
OL,15,F"violate" current legislation and
OL,16,F"ethical values".
