OL,6,FFollowing the filing of a legal
OL,7,Fcomplaint by the ADEE, the Ministry
OL,8,Fsaid the Director General for People
OL,9,Fwith Disabilities has "asked the
OL,10,FProsecutor's Office to investigate to
OL,11,Fdetermine whether the law and,
OL,12,Ftherefore, the rights of people with
OL,13,Fdisabilities have been violated."
