OL,3,CLamine Yamal could be investigated for
OL,4,Creportedly hiring people with dwarfism
OL,6,FIn a statement, ADEE's President
OL,7,FCarolina Puente said: "It's
OL,8,Funacceptable that in the 21st century,
OL,9,Fpeople with dwarfism continue to be
OL,10,Fused as entertainment at private
OL,11,Fparties, and even more serious when
OL,12,Fthese incidents involve public figures
OL,13,Flike Lamine Yamal.
OL,15,F"When a person with social influence
OL,16,Fparticipates in these types of
OL,17,Fsituations, the damage is even
OL,18,Fgreater, because it conveys to
OL,19,Fsociety`especially to young
OL,20,Fpeople`that discrimination is
OL,21,Facceptable.
